	.poll-header
		.poll-header-title
			div
				img(src='/static/imgs/polls/logo.svg').poll-header-logo
			h1.poll-title.poll-title--white
				span Vote for our next campaign
	
	.container
		if poll.closed
			.row
				.col-md-6
					h2.poll-title.poll-title--orange
						span Why did we do this?
					p
						img(src='/static/imgs/polls/box.svg').poll-ballot-box
						.
							We believe journalism isn’t just about information. It’s about
							empowering our communities and making a difference. In 2017 Bristol
							Cable members voted to create lasting change through dogged,
							creative and impactful campaigning journalism. Since then we have
							chalked up several wins. Over the past months, Cable members have
							contributed to planning our next campaign, and it’s now time to
							vote!

				.col-md-6
					h2.poll-title.poll-title--orange
						span The results
					.poll-result
						.poll-result-label
							b Campaign 1:
							br
							| Prevent drug deaths and clean up our streets
						.poll-result-bar
							.poll-result-bar2(style='width:' + (123/400*100) + '%')
							span 123 votes
					.poll-result
						.poll-result-label
							b Campaign 2:
							br
							| We want clean air. Lets fight for it
						.poll-result-bar
							.poll-result-bar2(style='width:' + (326/400*100) + '%')
							span 326 votes
