							We believe journalism isn’t just about information. It’s about
							empowering our communities and making a difference. In 2017 Bristol
							Cable members voted to create lasting change through dogged,
							creative and impactful campaigning journalism. Since then we have
							chalked up several wins. Over the past months, Cable members have
							contributed to planning our next campaign, and it’s now time to
							vote!

				.col-md-6.poll-actions
					.poll-action
						h2.poll-action-title
							span Are you a member?
